  "meta": {
    "title": "Arduino_AHRS_System",
    "description": "A compact realtime embedded Attitude and Heading Reference System (AHRS) using Recursive Least Squares (RLS) for magnetometer calibration and EKF/UKF for sensor fusion on Arduino platform ",
